N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 400.9 - Annual certification fee

State Regulations

On or before April 1st of each year, each certified capital company shall pay an annual, non- refundable certification fee of $500 to the superintendent, provided that no such fee shall be required within six months of the initial certification date of a certified capital company. Notes
